<TEXT>
MOODY'S Investors Service is reviewing the Aa3 senior unsecured debt rating
of Fujitsu, the Japanese computer group, for a possible downgrade, Reuter
reports from Tokyo. About Dollars 1.7bn of debt would be affected.
The action reflects Moody's concern that Fujitsu's low level of earnings and
