<HEADLINE>
FT  13 OCT 92 / International Company News: Recovery in demand lifts
earnings sharply at CPC
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By NIKKI TAIT
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
CPC International, the US food company whose products range from Hellmann's
mayonnaise to Knorr soups, saw after-tax profits rise from Dollars 75.5m to
