<TEXT>
There were 17,888 packages for the day, reports the Tea Brokers'
Association. Demand was good. Landed medium amd better quality Assams were
well supported at fully firm to dearer rates, but plainer sorts came to an
an easier market with some withdrawals. Brighter liquoring East Africans
